province(String, Model) - Method in class com.covid19app.ProvinceController
The province() method uses the @GetMapping() annotation to point to map the controller to the "/province" path of the URL and then takes in a model parameter which is used to model data in the Thymeleaf template.
ProvinceController - Class in com.covid19app
The ProvinceController is a controller for the News page which loads when the "/province" path is called in the URL and points to the province.html Thymeleaf template.
